step1:start the program
step2:read num1 and num2 from the user.
step3:add the values of num1 and num2 and store the result in num3
step4:display the value of num3
step5:stop

python code:
      num1=int(input("Enter the value for num1:"))
      num2=int(input("Enter the value for num2:"))
      num3=num1+num2
      print(num3)
